I knew you'd get somebody killed.

283
00:24:21,977 --> 00:24:24,241
Nobody really knows
what happened, okay?

284
00:24:24,980 --> 00:24:26,345
Come on, seriously.

285
00:24:27,382 --> 00:24:28,644
What's going on, Danny?

286
00:24:29,384 --> 00:24:30,817
We're hearing a lot of shit.

287
00:24:32,220 --> 00:24:33,209
What?

288
00:24:36,992 --> 00:24:38,220
Come on inside.

289
00:24:40,195 --> 00:24:42,663
All right, everybody, get back to work.

290
00:24:49,938 --> 00:24:51,132
Sit down.

291
00:24:55,677 --> 00:24:57,201
I'll be honest with you.

292
00:24:57,846 --> 00:24:59,837
I don't know what to think.

293
00:25:01,449 --> 00:25:04,543
