295
00:25:10,058 --> 00:25:11,889
So your gun and your badge.

296
00:25:17,432 --> 00:25:18,831
You know me.

297
00:25:20,669 --> 00:25:22,296
I'm being set up.

298
00:25:24,306 --> 00:25:26,467
Nate told me his informant
knows who's involved.

299
00:25:26,675 --> 00:25:29,803
Help me find this informant
and all this goes away.

300
00:27:03,338 --> 00:27:04,737
We should keep going.

301
00:27:05,540 --> 00:27:07,201
Mrs. Roenick, we should go.

302
00:27:08,543 --> 00:27:10,738
