304
00:27:12,914 --> 00:27:14,609
Fuck you, Danny.

305
00:27:15,684 --> 00:27:17,151
Fuck Niebaum.

306
00:27:17,585 --> 00:27:19,143
Fuck all of you.

307
00:27:19,487 --> 00:27:20,920
You all killed him.

308
00:27:21,823 --> 00:27:26,624
