You know how this city feels
about corrupt cops.

329
00:28:36,231 --> 00:28:38,426
I'll get a conviction
with my eyes closed.

330
00:28:39,067 --> 00:28:43,970
Tell us where the rest of the money is,
who your partners were and maybe...

331
00:28:44,439 --> 00:28:46,464
I need to speak to my client.

332
00:28:49,444 --> 00:28:51,605
I'll give you one day to make a deal.

333
00:28:52,480 --> 00:28:53,310
You hear me?

334
00:28:53,782 --> 00:28:54,908
One day.

335
00:28:55,316 --> 00:28:57,716
After that, there'll be no deal
to negotiate.

336
00:28:57,919 --> 00:29:01,878
